  "_meta": {
    "description": "NBA ingestion source registry. Tier 1 = league-wide insiders (Woj/Shams level, ~0.95 credibility). Tier 2 = team beat writers (~0.75). Tier 3 = aggregators / Reddit (~0.40). Twitter entries use the profile URL; the twitterWorker extracts the handle. RSS URLs should return a valid feed. Expand by copying an entry and flipping enabled=false for temporary disables.",
