    "pollingNotes": "Tier 1 polls every 2 min (aggressive — breaking news window). Tier 2 every 5 min. Tier 3 every 15 min. Actual poll cadence is ultimately gated by the master cron interval in src/index.ts (2 min), with per-source lastPolledAt used to skip sources that haven't hit their window yet."
  },
